WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 20]

01:18.800 --> 01:19.450
Qin.

01:20.080 --> 01:20.650
Qin.

01:21.000 --> 01:21.860
What happened to you?

01:22.390 --> 01:23.730
Did you get beaten up in your dream?

01:34.880 --> 01:35.530
I'm fine.

01:45.160 --> 01:45.700
Trouble!

01:46.190 --> 01:47.650
Demons are breaking the mountain-sea barrier.

01:48.310 --> 01:49.420
Return to the city at once

01:49.600 --> 01:50.420
and guard the people.

02:42.040 --> 02:43.060
The demon beast Qiongqi.

03:13.640 --> 03:15.740
[Qiongqi]
I'm Qiongqi. Greetings, My Lord.

03:18.670 --> 03:19.250
My Lord,

03:19.520 --> 03:20.500
you've finally returned.

03:21.830 --> 03:22.940
Is the lord you mentioned

03:24.320 --> 03:25.410
the Demon Lord Yecha?

03:25.870 --> 03:27.300
Word spread that you reappeared on the White Cliff.

03:27.590 --> 03:28.220
The whole demon clan

03:28.240 --> 03:29.780
longs for your arrival.

03:30.200 --> 03:31.650
After five centuries of exile and humiliation,

03:32.240 --> 03:34.130
we've dreamed of your return

03:34.360 --> 03:35.250
to restore our demon clan.

03:41.270 --> 03:42.300
I'm not your Demon Lord.

03:43.590 --> 03:44.500
Leave Duanming City

03:45.240 --> 03:46.340
with your followers at once.

03:47.640 --> 03:48.570
But the Guardians ordered...

03:52.200 --> 03:53.020
Yes, My Lord.

04:27.910 --> 04:28.570
Thank you.

04:50.710 --> 04:51.330
Tongzhou.

04:51.680 --> 04:52.130
Let's go.

05:06.150 --> 05:06.770
Uncle.

05:17.080 --> 05:17.770
What's this?

05:19.320 --> 05:20.300
The Four Symbols Divine Fire Formation.

06:08.960 --> 06:09.450
Medicine.

06:09.760 --> 06:10.420
Here.

06:12.910 --> 06:13.500
Are you alright?

06:14.200 --> 06:14.860
I'm fine.

06:18.910 --> 06:19.570
Move!

06:21.030 --> 06:21.660
Get up!

06:21.830 --> 06:23.130
Get up right now, you beast!

06:25.790 --> 06:26.660
Are you seeking death?

06:32.320 --> 06:33.540
- Get up. - Are you hurt?

06:37.120 --> 06:37.690
Who's there?

06:39.880 --> 06:40.810
It's just a cub.

06:41.120 --> 06:42.010
Doesn't seem to have killed anyone.

06:42.030 --> 06:42.660
Why slay it?

06:44.320 --> 06:45.300
You

06:45.560 --> 06:47.420
spared that little beast last time!

06:47.790 --> 06:48.210
You...

06:48.680 --> 06:49.180
All of you

06:49.560 --> 06:51.100
are in league with the monster beast.

06:52.320 --> 06:53.540
Bully the weak

06:53.560 --> 06:54.450
and twist the truth, huh?

06:54.790 --> 06:57.180
Duanming City used to live in peace.

06:57.470 --> 06:58.570
Ever since you showed up,

06:58.960 --> 06:59.770
either the barrier breaks

06:59.790 --> 07:00.770
or demon beasts run amok.

07:00.960 --> 07:02.370
How can you deny you're spies?

07:02.830 --> 07:04.010
What do you mean?

07:04.520 --> 07:05.450
We've worked tirelessly

07:05.470 --> 07:06.500
to subdue monsters and calm chaos.

07:06.790 --> 07:08.130
How dare you slander us?

07:08.640 --> 07:10.690
Everyone knows Mountain Sect's disciples are crafty.

07:11.200 --> 07:12.690
Chances are, you came to the East Sea

07:13.200 --> 07:15.660
with malicious intent to stir trouble.

07:15.880 --> 07:16.690
Watch your words!

07:16.710 --> 07:17.740
You slander us out of thin air!

07:17.790 --> 07:19.010
This is the Sea Sect's territory.

07:19.030 --> 07:19.890
Leave at once!

07:23.880 --> 07:24.620
Silence!

07:32.710 --> 07:33.980
Among these captured monster beasts,

07:34.560 --> 07:36.100
some are spirit companions raised by the Sea Sect.

07:36.640 --> 07:37.660
There is a hidden truth behind this chaos.

07:38.320 --> 07:39.660
The Guangsheng Faction only detains them,

07:40.200 --> 07:41.180
with no authority to pass judgment.

07:44.200 --> 07:46.770
Mr. Shen and the immortal elders haven't looked into this yet.

07:47.270 --> 07:48.940
You're trying to kill them to cover up the truth, huh?

07:49.880 --> 07:50.620
Fine, forget it.

07:50.880 --> 07:51.890
Let's go.

07:52.790 --> 07:53.660
Move, follow me.

07:54.640 --> 07:55.100
Come.

07:56.120 --> 07:56.570
Go.

07:57.150 --> 07:57.810
Hurry up!

07:58.200 --> 07:58.660
Faster!

08:00.270 --> 08:00.860
Quick!

08:03.790 --> 08:04.420
Be careful.

08:06.880 --> 08:07.570
Behave yourselves.

08:07.760 --> 08:08.210
Hurry.

08:08.880 --> 08:09.690
I'll follow them to watch them,

08:10.030 --> 08:11.060
in case they stir up more trouble.

08:18.890 --> 08:20.080
[Duanming City Inn]

08:20.080 --> 08:22.300
You know that cultivating the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

08:22.390 --> 08:23.740
requires severing all mortal affection.

08:24.470 --> 08:26.300
Yet only a few days after arriving in Duanming City,

08:26.910 --> 08:28.300
your spirit sense has sustained damage,

08:28.470 --> 08:29.660
and a heart tribulation looms over you.

08:30.440 --> 08:32.010
Is it because of Jiang Lifei?

08:33.390 --> 08:34.370
I let my guard down for a moment.

08:34.910 --> 08:35.740
It has nothing to do with her.

08:36.710 --> 08:38.970
Besides, she's far stronger now.

08:39.110 --> 08:39.940
Her cultivation has advanced greatly,

08:40.280 --> 08:41.450
and she saved me on Fanghu Island.

08:44.470 --> 08:45.300
Tongzhou,

08:45.960 --> 08:49.690
the Xuanhua Sacred Fire is the Hua Sect's supreme technique.

08:50.160 --> 08:52.450
No one has mastered it in hundreds of years,

08:53.920 --> 08:55.180
not even me.

08:57.320 --> 08:59.610
If you cannot cast aside personal desires

08:59.630 --> 09:00.690
and master the Sacred Fire,

09:01.440 --> 09:04.140
how will you lead Xingzheng Hall

09:04.630 --> 09:07.570
and fulfill the grand plan to secure Yue's realm?

09:09.040 --> 09:10.420
I'll master the supreme technique.

09:11.200 --> 09:12.210
You have my word.

09:14.660 --> 09:15.140
But

09:17.110 --> 09:18.330
I'll never give up Jiang Lifei.

09:18.830 --> 09:20.020
In your life,

09:20.320 --> 09:21.730
you gain only after you let go.

09:21.980 --> 09:22.900
The immortal path is lonely.

09:22.920 --> 09:24.140
How can you have both?

09:24.580 --> 09:25.380
Whether I can have both,

09:26.230 --> 09:27.300
I'll have my own judgment.

09:29.040 --> 09:30.810
No need to lecture me

09:31.200 --> 09:32.060
over and over.

09:34.470 --> 09:35.300
Very well.

09:38.590 --> 09:39.780
If you insist on this foolish path,

09:40.110 --> 09:40.690
so be it.

09:42.320 --> 09:45.690
I'll wait for the day you hit a dead end

09:46.470 --> 09:48.380
and damage your cultivation.

09:50.540 --> 09:51.180
Tongzhou,

09:51.630 --> 09:52.690
here's the antidote to the monster poison...

09:54.400 --> 09:55.210
Mr. Xuanshan.

10:08.820 --> 10:10.090
He's so furious.

10:14.590 --> 10:16.140
Still because of the mirage dream?

10:17.300 --> 10:18.330
What did you see?

10:19.180 --> 10:20.180
Are you still under its influence?

10:23.060 --> 10:24.490
All those illusions are fake.

10:24.980 --> 10:26.380
Dwelling on them, and you'll lose yourself.

10:26.420 --> 10:27.020
I'm not dwelling on it.

10:29.110 --> 10:29.970
You don't understand.

10:31.060 --> 10:31.850
Don't understand?

10:32.340 --> 10:34.330
Because I don't dwell on painful memories.

10:34.990 --> 10:36.300
Dreams show the opposite of reality.

10:36.560 --> 10:37.490
Try to look on the bright side,

10:37.680 --> 10:38.780
and they might be a good sign.

10:40.420 --> 10:41.210
A good sign?

10:42.750 --> 10:43.420
Think about it.

10:43.870 --> 10:44.780
The illusion laid out

10:44.820 --> 10:46.260
all your deepest fears,

10:46.470 --> 10:48.180
so you can avoid them in the real world.

10:49.340 --> 10:51.090
At the very least,

10:51.110 --> 10:52.660
you won't feel as helpless as you did in the illusion.

10:55.750 --> 10:56.330
Lifei,

10:58.350 --> 11:00.900
if one day a great disaster befalls me,

11:01.510 --> 11:02.180
or

11:03.180 --> 11:04.380
I lose everything

11:04.940 --> 11:05.690
and am left all alone,

11:06.940 --> 11:07.940
would you abandon me?

11:08.940 --> 11:09.940
Your Highness, do not abandon us,

11:09.980 --> 11:11.090
your friends.

11:25.100 --> 11:25.810
How's Tongzhou?

11:28.830 --> 11:29.490
He's alright,

11:30.340 --> 11:31.570
just acting a little strange.

11:32.990 --> 11:34.660
Probably the mirage dream scared him badly.

11:37.510 --> 11:38.140
By the way,

11:38.710 --> 11:40.490
did you catch demon beast Qiongqi?

11:42.060 --> 11:44.210
It got away.

11:45.420 --> 11:46.690
If it escaped your grasp,

11:47.230 --> 11:48.780
it must be extremely powerful.

11:50.590 --> 11:53.020
I wonder how many demon beasts are in the city.

12:02.420 --> 12:04.140
You are fiery

12:04.340 --> 12:06.180
and passionate.

12:06.220 --> 12:07.210
Your cultivation

12:07.300 --> 12:09.260
will surely be fraught with hardships.

12:09.470 --> 12:11.420
All love, hatred, grudges, entanglements,

12:11.460 --> 12:12.570
and the bustling mortal world

12:12.590 --> 12:14.180
will stoke an unquenchable inner flame.

12:14.300 --> 12:15.660
If you cannot let go,

12:15.830 --> 12:17.210
how can you make progress?

12:18.590 --> 12:19.300
Tongzhou.

12:20.870 --> 12:21.570
Lifei.

12:42.710 --> 12:43.690
Dwelling on them,

12:43.710 --> 12:44.690
and you'll lose yourself.

12:47.110 --> 12:48.180
It is a fleeting dream,

12:48.510 --> 12:49.300
all fake.

12:49.830 --> 12:50.610
Let it go.

12:57.280 --> 12:57.850
Lifei.

13:19.350 --> 13:19.850
Speak!

13:20.200 --> 13:21.690
Who ordered you to stir up trouble?

13:22.470 --> 13:24.970
You humans are selfish and hypocritical.

13:25.320 --> 13:26.660
You oppress the monster clan

13:27.040 --> 13:28.300
and slaughter us at will.

13:28.800 --> 13:30.060
We only fled for our lives.

13:30.280 --> 13:31.540
What's wrong with that?

13:31.800 --> 13:33.210
What's wrong with that?

13:48.990 --> 13:51.610
So it's possessed by the demon clan.

13:53.400 --> 13:53.970
Speak!

13:54.590 --> 13:55.140
Monster,

13:56.230 --> 13:57.940
who is your demon leader?

13:58.680 --> 13:59.610
Old fool.

14:00.040 --> 14:01.210
The Demon Lord has returned.

14:01.510 --> 14:02.970
The Guardians' schemes are flawless.

14:03.350 --> 14:05.810
Soon we'll conquer the Central Plains

14:06.040 --> 14:08.300
and slay every last one of you.

14:13.920 --> 14:15.210
Which Guardian?

14:16.280 --> 14:18.300
Are they hiding in the city now?

14:24.510 --> 14:25.660
Five centuries ago,

14:25.990 --> 14:28.970
I fought two Guardians of the demon clan.

14:29.280 --> 14:30.570
They were extremely crafty.

14:31.230 --> 14:32.490
Whichever one has sneaked in,

14:33.040 --> 14:34.810
they will prove a deadly foe.

14:36.680 --> 14:37.300
Mr. Shen,

14:37.710 --> 14:39.730
we can't question every

14:39.750 --> 14:40.540
captured monster beast.

14:40.920 --> 14:41.730
In my opinion,

14:42.080 --> 14:43.420
we may execute all of them together

14:43.440 --> 14:44.300
to eliminate future threats.

14:46.920 --> 14:47.490
Lifei!

14:48.710 --> 14:49.330
Lifei!

14:50.830 --> 14:51.450
It's terrible!

14:51.920 --> 14:52.900
Elder Cuixuan has ordered

14:52.990 --> 14:54.940
that all captured monster beasts must be killed.

14:57.110 --> 14:58.260
Did they find the demon leader?

14:58.470 --> 14:59.780
Why kill the monster clan suddenly?

15:01.870 --> 15:03.780
Last night, I went to the Guangsheng Faction's prison

15:04.280 --> 15:06.260
to make sure they wouldn't kill the spirits.

15:06.750 --> 15:08.060
But when I came back this morning,

15:08.440 --> 15:10.020
Luo Chengji's disciples passed down the order

15:10.510 --> 15:12.380
to transfer all monster beasts to the shore

15:12.680 --> 15:13.610
and kill them all,

15:13.870 --> 15:14.690
none spared.

15:23.830 --> 15:24.540
Deng,

15:25.800 --> 15:26.570
what are you doing?

15:27.560 --> 15:28.210
Step out here!

15:38.400 --> 15:40.810
You're hiding a spirit right under the elder's nose.

15:41.350 --> 15:42.420
Are you seeking death?

15:44.350 --> 15:45.900
I saved this little one before.

15:46.160 --> 15:47.610
It risked its life to save me yesterday

15:47.920 --> 15:49.380
and is sharing key information with us.

15:51.960 --> 15:54.490
That day, after Lifei saved me,

15:54.960 --> 15:55.810
I planned to head back

15:55.830 --> 15:57.780
to my homeland, Yingcui Island, with my elders.

15:58.040 --> 15:59.210
But before we left the city,

15:59.440 --> 16:01.140
all the spirit beasts around suddenly went berserk,

16:01.470 --> 16:02.850
and my elders lost their minds too.

16:03.230 --> 16:04.380
I tried to hold them back,

16:04.510 --> 16:05.690
yet they acted as if they didn't know me

16:05.710 --> 16:06.690
and even tried to kill me.

16:06.870 --> 16:07.810
Terrified,

16:07.830 --> 16:08.780
I hid myself away,

16:09.110 --> 16:10.490
and that's when I met Lifei.

16:12.710 --> 16:14.420
Spirit companions may have faint power,

16:14.710 --> 16:16.140
yet they possess some cultivation.

16:16.590 --> 16:18.490
Why are they controlled by the demon clan so easily?

16:23.750 --> 16:24.450
Before they lost control,

16:24.800 --> 16:26.570
did you eat or drink anything?

16:27.230 --> 16:29.610
To avoid being captured again by the Guangsheng Faction,

16:29.960 --> 16:31.060
we didn't even have time to eat.

16:31.230 --> 16:33.140
They drank water from a pond along the way.

16:33.560 --> 16:34.450
I had a mouth wound

16:35.080 --> 16:36.060
and dared not touch the water.

16:37.400 --> 16:38.330
Now it all makes sense.

16:38.870 --> 16:39.850
I was wondering

16:40.400 --> 16:42.140
how the demon clan could seize

16:42.350 --> 16:44.060
all the monster beasts in the city overnight

16:44.080 --> 16:46.610
under the immortal elders' noses.

16:46.830 --> 16:48.180
That would only alert us.

16:50.630 --> 16:52.020
There's only one explanation.

16:54.320 --> 16:55.450
The water source is poisoned.

16:55.560 --> 16:57.090
Yeah, they poisoned the water supply.

17:06.710 --> 17:07.850
I've asked Gelin.

17:08.230 --> 17:09.730
All underground water in Duanming City

17:09.750 --> 17:10.820
connects to this freshwater lake.

17:11.310 --> 17:12.290
If someone wants to poison the water,

17:12.510 --> 17:13.730
this place will be the perfect spot.

17:34.710 --> 17:35.450
They're from the Guangsheng Faction.

17:36.440 --> 17:36.940
Mr. Shi,

17:37.310 --> 17:38.690
I've spread all the sea salt.

17:39.200 --> 17:40.860
After killing every monster beast tomorrow morning,

17:41.310 --> 17:42.660
we'll strip their hides

17:42.680 --> 17:43.620
and cure their flesh.

17:43.990 --> 17:46.380
Not a single hair will go to waste, I promise you.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.420
Seems that the man told me the truth.

17:49.270 --> 17:50.340
Wait till you return to tally your gold.

17:50.710 --> 17:51.180
Let's go.

17:52.160 --> 17:52.620
What if

17:52.840 --> 17:54.100
that old fool changes his mind

17:54.230 --> 17:55.050
and calls off the slaughter?

17:55.600 --> 17:56.180
He won't.

17:56.600 --> 17:57.900
The immortal sects mean to bait someone out,

17:57.920 --> 17:59.250
so they'll kill without mercy.

17:59.600 --> 18:00.250
Hurry, let's go.

18:08.070 --> 18:09.250
Spirit-Releasing Antidote Powder.

18:11.310 --> 18:12.770
It's Shi Chengtian's doing, just as expected.

18:13.750 --> 18:14.620
I'm going to Mr. Shen.

18:16.680 --> 18:17.140
Don't bother.

18:17.880 --> 18:18.690
To them,

18:19.310 --> 18:20.140
the truth means nothing.

18:21.920 --> 18:22.660
The elders know full well what caused

18:23.310 --> 18:25.010
the monster beasts to lose control.

18:26.270 --> 18:27.530
They're using it to eliminate all non-human creatures

18:27.960 --> 18:28.730
and future threats for good.

18:30.230 --> 18:31.140
All lives are precious.

18:31.710 --> 18:32.380
They have no right to decide

18:32.400 --> 18:33.730
the fate of these innocent monster beasts.

18:35.640 --> 18:36.490
As the monster beasts ran amok,

18:37.400 --> 18:39.210
slaying them is what everyone wants.

18:39.840 --> 18:40.900
If you speak up for them,

18:41.340 --> 18:42.100
be ready

18:42.750 --> 18:44.210
to openly stand against the immortal sects.

18:44.960 --> 18:45.690
Do you understand?

18:46.880 --> 18:47.420
I do.

18:48.470 --> 18:50.050
At worst, I'll be barred from returning to Wuyue Court.

18:51.070 --> 18:52.490
If they can't tell right from wrong

18:52.510 --> 18:53.290
and kill the innocent,

18:53.920 --> 18:55.380
I won't care to remain their disciple.

18:55.990 --> 18:56.660
In that case,

18:56.960 --> 18:58.050
we can return to the Chufeng Academy.

18:58.550 --> 18:59.180
Master...

19:00.270 --> 19:00.860
Mr. Hu

19:01.400 --> 19:02.970
and Mr. Zuo Qiu will take us in.

19:04.600 --> 19:05.210
Lifei,

19:05.880 --> 19:06.660
count me in, too!

19:07.160 --> 19:08.010
Count me in, too!

19:10.030 --> 19:11.620
Don't get mixed up in this.

19:13.160 --> 19:14.100
How can I be your senior

19:14.270 --> 19:15.660
and stand aside?

19:16.600 --> 19:17.970
Besides, what are you off to do?

19:18.840 --> 19:20.690
Save all living beings!

19:21.120 --> 19:23.250
It's such a meritorious deed.

19:23.680 --> 19:27.050
I might even ascend to immortality from this.

19:27.510 --> 19:28.250
You must count me in.

19:31.200 --> 19:31.940
This journey will be dangerous,

19:32.880 --> 19:33.660
so you may back out at any time

19:34.640 --> 19:35.210
if you regret it.

19:38.160 --> 19:39.420
- I'll never regret it.
- I'll never regret it.

19:45.120 --> 19:46.250
Everyone, good work out there.

19:46.790 --> 19:48.490
Mr. Shi sends his regards.

19:56.440 --> 19:57.210
It didn't work at all.

20:03.660 --> 20:04.490
I knew it.

20:04.990 --> 20:05.730
Mr. Dongyang refined

20:05.750 --> 20:07.580
this drug from sleep-inducing bugs,

20:07.620 --> 20:08.820
so it can knock them all out.

20:09.700 --> 20:10.140
Go.

20:14.710 --> 20:15.820
Wuyue Court's restriction spell.

20:16.460 --> 20:17.770
What do we do now?

20:18.360 --> 20:19.180
What can we do?

20:20.180 --> 20:20.860
I know how to break it.

20:22.070 --> 20:22.580
Then...

20:24.900 --> 20:25.730
All arts converge as one;

20:25.940 --> 20:26.730
break the formation and reveal the spirit.

20:30.310 --> 20:31.770
You've got real skill.

20:31.790 --> 20:32.490
Naturally.

20:32.900 --> 20:34.730
Since I was taken as my master's personal disciple at three,

20:35.030 --> 20:36.420
I've tinkered with these formations for over a decade.

20:36.510 --> 20:37.380
Child's play for me.

20:38.550 --> 20:38.940
Let's go.

20:38.990 --> 20:39.420
Hurry.

20:59.310 --> 21:01.100
As the mirage poison lingers in your body for ages,

21:02.750 --> 21:04.450
your spirit roots are damaged now.

21:06.600 --> 21:07.820
It may take a decade

21:08.900 --> 21:11.770
to fully mend them.

21:13.550 --> 21:14.660
Darn it.

21:15.230 --> 21:16.140
I'm incompetent

21:17.620 --> 21:19.100
and have troubled you greatly.

21:19.790 --> 21:21.580
Focus solely on recuperating for now.

21:21.940 --> 21:22.580
Once we return,

21:23.790 --> 21:26.530
I'll have Dongyang tend to your conditioning carefully.

21:27.180 --> 21:28.100
Thank you, Master.

21:28.940 --> 21:29.580
Master,

21:30.270 --> 21:31.250
during our time on Fanghu Island,

21:31.470 --> 21:32.660
I discovered that Jiang Lifei...

21:37.460 --> 21:38.770
There's a jailbreak rescue!

21:43.510 --> 21:44.250
Halt!

21:45.230 --> 21:47.180
You should guard the outside.

21:47.310 --> 21:48.420
Why have you come in?

21:48.860 --> 21:49.770
Any more drugs left?

21:49.790 --> 21:50.580
I've given you all of it.

21:52.660 --> 21:54.180
I came inside to relieve myself

21:54.460 --> 21:55.180
and will head out right away.

21:56.660 --> 21:57.420
- You... - He's far too strong.

21:57.460 --> 21:58.530
I'll fetch reinforcements. Hold him off.

21:58.550 --> 21:59.180
What a fair-weather friend.

22:00.070 --> 22:01.490
Are you also here to relieve yourself?

22:03.990 --> 22:05.690
I came along with him. I'm leaving.

22:05.990 --> 22:06.900
Jiang Lifei.

22:12.990 --> 22:15.290
You have sharp eyes and saw

22:15.510 --> 22:17.530
right through my disguise at once.

22:18.940 --> 22:20.450
Why are you dressed like this?

22:23.420 --> 22:25.820
I heard the monster beast chaos

22:25.860 --> 22:27.450
was stirred up by demon spies.

22:28.220 --> 22:29.290
So I thought

22:29.310 --> 22:30.100
if I dressed like this,

22:30.120 --> 22:31.620
I could capture and question a monster beast,

22:31.940 --> 22:33.250
so I could help you capture

22:33.270 --> 22:34.620
demon spies ahead of time.

22:35.270 --> 22:38.010
She is cunning and will become a grave threat.

22:42.160 --> 22:43.100
He's trying to kill me!

22:44.420 --> 22:45.690
I... I have

22:46.600 --> 22:47.690
a terrible stomachache.

22:47.710 --> 22:49.290
May I step aside for a moment?

22:49.900 --> 22:50.530
Stomachache?

22:50.900 --> 22:52.450
Then let me check your pulse.

22:59.180 --> 23:01.140
I'm sacrificing myself to save them!

23:01.620 --> 23:03.730
Xiuyuan, everything rests on you.

23:22.180 --> 23:22.690
Lu.

23:28.660 --> 23:29.290
Clan leader.

23:31.860 --> 23:32.450
Clan leader?

23:34.270 --> 23:35.100
I'm a half-monster.

23:36.070 --> 23:38.660
They are my clansfolk.

23:39.180 --> 23:40.690
I never thought disciples of the immortal sects

23:40.990 --> 23:42.530
would lend a hand to the monster clan.

23:43.310 --> 23:43.940
Lei,

23:44.990 --> 23:45.530
thank you.

23:48.790 --> 23:50.140
The elders will find out soon.

23:50.940 --> 23:51.690
We have to leave at once.

23:55.550 --> 23:56.420
I'm at my limit.

23:56.710 --> 23:57.250
I'll risk everything!

24:05.230 --> 24:06.250
An empty shell.

24:07.120 --> 24:08.100
You were testing me.

24:08.470 --> 24:09.900
You've got some perseverance.

24:17.310 --> 24:18.940
So you really came to rescue them.

24:21.660 --> 24:22.180
Uncle!

24:24.470 --> 24:25.250
Tongzhou?

24:25.470 --> 24:26.050
Uncle,

24:26.460 --> 24:27.420
this whole thing was my idea.

24:27.700 --> 24:28.660
I told Lifei to...

24:28.860 --> 24:30.290
To meet you.

24:33.750 --> 24:34.970
Since His Highness is here,

24:34.990 --> 24:37.010
I'll speak plainly.

24:37.270 --> 24:38.050
What are you doing?

24:38.660 --> 24:40.660
Since His Highness got injured yesterday,

24:41.070 --> 24:42.730
I've been consumed with guilt.

24:43.220 --> 24:44.580
I feared you'd hold a grudge against me.

24:45.460 --> 24:46.530
But His Highness said

24:47.070 --> 24:49.050
you're the kindest,

24:49.220 --> 24:50.690
and you won't hold this against me.

24:51.220 --> 24:52.490
So I ventured here

24:52.510 --> 24:53.690
to explain myself.

24:53.710 --> 24:54.380
Uncle,

25:00.680 --> 25:03.620
please allow us to be cultivation partners.

25:13.160 --> 25:13.690
Lifei,

25:15.230 --> 25:17.690
we've sworn to never abandon one another.

25:18.440 --> 25:20.420
My uncle won't make things hard for you.

25:21.230 --> 25:22.770
Take out the token I gave you.

25:24.960 --> 25:25.730
The Chiyan Stone.

25:27.710 --> 25:29.660
It's here.

25:30.270 --> 25:30.940
Here.

25:33.400 --> 25:35.420
You gave the Zhurong Stone to an outsider?

25:37.710 --> 25:39.620
This is the Zhurong Stone?

25:40.510 --> 25:41.100
Watch out!

25:44.160 --> 25:44.660
Go!

25:45.600 --> 25:46.250
Take care!

25:47.200 --> 25:47.820
Tongzhou,

25:48.790 --> 25:50.420
you dare raise a hand against me?

25:50.960 --> 25:51.660
Calm your anger.

25:52.680 --> 25:53.940
Lifei is no outsider.

25:54.960 --> 25:56.580
She is my cultivation partner who shares life and death with me.

25:57.640 --> 25:59.690
Please grant us your permission.

26:02.070 --> 26:03.490
[Guangsheng Faction]
We're finally out.

26:04.200 --> 26:05.050
Hurry up!

26:15.710 --> 26:17.050
Mere petty trickery.

26:18.440 --> 26:19.050
Reveal your form!

26:31.070 --> 26:32.180
Over there! Chase!

26:32.310 --> 26:33.050
Yes!

26:49.920 --> 26:51.140
They're somewhere nearby.

27:01.270 --> 27:01.900
Mr. Luo,

27:02.270 --> 27:02.770
monster beasts

27:03.680 --> 27:04.690
are trying to kill me.

27:04.710 --> 27:05.380
Where

27:06.030 --> 27:06.770
are they?

27:07.680 --> 27:08.340
Over there!

27:18.070 --> 27:19.140
There's evil spiritual energy

27:20.960 --> 27:22.100
all over you.

27:27.270 --> 27:29.690
I must have gotten monster blood on myself

27:30.100 --> 27:31.140
while fighting them earlier.

27:31.920 --> 27:32.420
Master,

27:32.510 --> 27:33.380
monster beasts are over there!

27:34.960 --> 27:35.820
Right there, let's check it out.

27:35.990 --> 27:37.140
- Go. - Chase!

27:52.310 --> 27:53.100
Dawn is breaking soon.

27:53.550 --> 27:54.620
Are you sure we can get out this way?

27:54.790 --> 27:56.380
There is a secret door under the jar fortress.

27:56.400 --> 27:57.210
We'll make it out for sure.

28:04.840 --> 28:05.420
Leave it to me.

28:21.840 --> 28:22.730
This aura...

28:27.550 --> 28:29.210
Jiang Lifei.

28:29.230 --> 28:29.940
Let them pass.

28:40.070 --> 28:41.180
The trip is dangerous.

28:42.600 --> 28:43.210
Take care.

28:44.160 --> 28:44.660
Will do.

28:53.550 --> 28:53.940
Hurry!

29:01.920 --> 29:03.100
What's going on here?

29:05.360 --> 29:06.250
What happened?

29:08.710 --> 29:09.660
I let my guard down.

29:10.840 --> 29:12.490
They mean to hunt us all down,

29:12.990 --> 29:13.770
leaving none alive.

29:15.120 --> 29:17.580
Fire! Look, there's fire!

29:18.710 --> 29:19.290
Fire!

29:25.160 --> 29:25.940
Everyone, stay calm.

29:26.880 --> 29:27.490
Mr. Lu,

29:27.600 --> 29:28.900
we signed a spirit pact

29:28.920 --> 29:30.490
to live in peace alongside humans.

29:30.640 --> 29:31.770
Why do they seek to slay us,

29:31.990 --> 29:33.530
even leaving our bodies unburied?

29:33.680 --> 29:34.970
The formation won't hold much longer. What to do?

29:35.270 --> 29:35.940
I'll hold them off.

29:36.400 --> 29:38.050
Lead everyone away with Lu Li.

29:38.750 --> 29:39.490
I'm staying here with you.

29:40.070 --> 29:40.580
Lifei.

29:40.790 --> 29:41.730
Don't you act on your own.

29:42.120 --> 29:43.140
The Fragrance Bond still binds us.

29:43.550 --> 29:44.340
We swore

29:44.790 --> 29:46.900
to live and die together, never to abandon each other.

29:47.230 --> 29:48.340
Neither of us shall break that.

29:54.440 --> 29:55.490
[Riyan, Nine-Tailed Fox]
It's so hot in here.

29:56.710 --> 29:58.180
What are you roasting?

29:59.710 --> 30:00.900
Riyan, you've healed up.

30:01.200 --> 30:01.860
Please,

30:02.120 --> 30:03.100
let us get out of here.

30:04.470 --> 30:05.140
I'll give it a shot.

30:18.880 --> 30:19.820
It's the mountain-sea barrier.

30:21.160 --> 30:21.940
I can't break through.

30:37.710 --> 30:39.340
The old monster is here too.

31:02.470 --> 31:03.010
Wait for me!

31:03.880 --> 31:04.660
Just listen to me.

31:04.680 --> 31:05.290
Don't touch me.

31:07.070 --> 31:08.250
Riyan.

31:09.160 --> 31:10.050
Riyan,

31:10.510 --> 31:12.380
could you teach me

31:12.440 --> 31:13.620
the Divine Brush Teleportation skill?

31:14.550 --> 31:16.530
Old monster, mind your own business!

31:16.680 --> 31:17.580
You're stealing my spotlight!

31:18.160 --> 31:19.900
Fox, you're truly ungrateful.

31:20.710 --> 31:22.490
I went out of my way to help you,

31:23.070 --> 31:24.380
yet you won't even say thank you.

31:25.510 --> 31:26.620
Mr. Yan.

31:27.470 --> 31:28.340
Lifei,

31:28.470 --> 31:30.730
we're fated to cross paths from afar.

31:31.030 --> 31:32.860
It'd be such a waste not to strike it rich together.

31:33.030 --> 31:34.180
You stinky old monster!

31:37.920 --> 31:38.580
Mr. Yan,

31:39.880 --> 31:40.730
what are you doing here?

31:41.470 --> 31:42.860
Lately, folks are on edge,

31:42.880 --> 31:43.770
and business has been slow,

31:43.990 --> 31:46.100
so I plan to travel overseas

31:46.680 --> 31:48.340
to gather material for new tales.

31:50.840 --> 31:51.490
Mr. Yan,

31:52.710 --> 31:55.100
are you also a monster?

31:58.440 --> 32:01.420
Anything abnormal is labeled as a monster.

32:02.030 --> 32:02.940
In that sense,

32:04.120 --> 32:05.450
we're all monsters.

32:05.750 --> 32:06.420
True.

32:06.960 --> 32:07.970
None of us fit the norm,

32:08.200 --> 32:09.010
so we're all monsters alike.

32:10.600 --> 32:11.250
Mr. Yan,

32:11.550 --> 32:12.290
what kind of monster are you?

32:13.710 --> 32:15.690
Your mastery over script spirit is peerless,

32:16.070 --> 32:17.490
so you must possess a semi-immortal body,

32:18.030 --> 32:19.970
knowing all under heaven.

32:23.550 --> 32:24.690
Does that mean

32:25.360 --> 32:26.770
all script spirits obey your will?

32:27.230 --> 32:28.690
No wonder you're skilled at spinning tales.

32:33.920 --> 32:36.340
I'm deeply grateful to all of you for your help.

32:36.550 --> 32:38.380
I'll lead my clansmen to Yingcui Island to settle down.

32:38.960 --> 32:39.730
Farewell for now.

32:42.880 --> 32:45.860
Yingcui Island belongs to that great bird.

32:46.600 --> 32:48.180
Are you its descendant?

32:49.510 --> 32:50.860
I'm Lu Li, leader of the Jiufeng Clan,

32:51.230 --> 32:52.530
half-monster.

32:54.270 --> 32:55.660
Yingcui Island is thousands of miles away.

32:55.990 --> 32:57.210
You'll struggle to travel there.

32:57.550 --> 32:59.530
I'll give you a ride.

33:00.880 --> 33:01.690
Thanks, Mr. Yan.

33:02.200 --> 33:02.730
Old coot,

33:03.120 --> 33:04.010
you're tagging along.

33:04.470 --> 33:06.770
I'm going overseas to find answers.

33:08.600 --> 33:09.210
Young man,

33:10.270 --> 33:10.940
come over here.

33:11.270 --> 33:12.530
I need a word with you.

33:26.070 --> 33:27.490
You've got your old memories back,

33:28.710 --> 33:30.340
so you know who she is, right?

33:33.310 --> 33:34.210
So what if I know?

33:36.600 --> 33:37.450
I've only ever wanted her

33:37.920 --> 33:39.140
from day one.

33:39.920 --> 33:41.210
Can you protect her?

33:42.070 --> 33:42.900
You just want to

33:43.600 --> 33:45.290
lock her up for yourself.

33:46.360 --> 33:47.690
Your so-called love

33:48.070 --> 33:49.140
is poisoning her.

33:49.470 --> 33:50.420
Things will be different in this life.

33:52.360 --> 33:53.450
She might believe you

33:54.070 --> 33:55.100
a few times,

33:56.920 --> 33:58.620
but she'll see through you eventually.

34:03.030 --> 34:03.730
Riyan,

34:05.230 --> 34:06.180
you misunderstand her.

34:08.790 --> 34:09.820
Lifei is far from foolish.

34:11.120 --> 34:12.010
At times,

34:13.110 --> 34:14.010
she is even wiser than I am

34:15.510 --> 34:16.450
and is clear about her choices.

34:23.920 --> 34:24.820
Mark my words.

34:25.280 --> 34:26.970
If she suffers even the slightest injury,

34:29.510 --> 34:31.050
I will hold you accountable.

34:38.590 --> 34:39.530
Rest assured.

34:39.960 --> 34:41.700
I'll protect her with all I have.

34:47.800 --> 34:49.170
What are you two whispering about?

34:51.440 --> 34:52.940
You don't want to leave me?

34:53.630 --> 34:55.090
When I first met you,

34:55.510 --> 34:56.490
you were a fool.

34:57.380 --> 34:58.650
Now that I'm leaving,

34:59.340 --> 35:00.380
you still are.

35:03.240 --> 35:04.860
Just say it if you'll miss me.

35:05.590 --> 35:06.340
Enough,

35:06.470 --> 35:07.130
old fox.

35:07.420 --> 35:08.340
Let's go.

35:08.820 --> 35:10.380
Young folks have their own paths to walk.

35:10.780 --> 35:12.530
Let's stay out of this.

35:13.670 --> 35:14.300
True.

35:15.190 --> 35:15.970
I've slept far too long.

35:16.900 --> 35:18.780
Time to stretch my limbs.

35:30.780 --> 35:31.490
Girl,

35:31.670 --> 35:32.700
on your way back,

35:32.780 --> 35:34.260
visit the East Sea's cliff inscriptions.

35:36.110 --> 35:37.420
Did you leave a treasure for me?

35:50.670 --> 35:53.050
I wonder if Lifei managed to escape.

35:54.670 --> 35:55.380
Don't worry.

35:56.110 --> 35:57.130
She'll be fine

35:57.300 --> 35:58.380
with Xiuyuan by her side.

36:06.820 --> 36:07.740
Jiao said a witness

36:08.340 --> 36:10.220
claimed Lifei helped the monster clan run off.

36:11.900 --> 36:12.820
We promised we wouldn't...

36:17.380 --> 36:18.940
We promised we wouldn't leave any clues.

36:19.070 --> 36:19.780
Who ratted them out?

36:20.150 --> 36:21.010
No matter who it is,

36:21.470 --> 36:22.860
Lifei will be in trouble if she comes back.

36:26.590 --> 36:27.610
Then she'd better stay away

36:28.190 --> 36:29.700
and lie low somewhere.

36:31.980 --> 36:32.650
I'll go and find her.

36:54.590 --> 36:56.530
Our trip begins at Mount Man by the East Sea.

36:56.940 --> 36:58.300
Boundless ocean spreads out.

36:58.470 --> 36:59.780
By Qingcheng of Wuyue Court

37:00.300 --> 37:02.450
and Riyan of Qingqiu.

37:03.720 --> 37:06.130
Riyan was actually close with Elder Qingcheng.

37:07.820 --> 37:09.130
I never heard this before.

37:16.110 --> 37:18.170
Where do you reckon Elder Qingcheng ended up later?

37:19.190 --> 37:20.490
My master said

37:20.820 --> 37:22.340
he invented the Five Turtle Technique.

37:27.900 --> 37:28.610
It's late.

37:29.380 --> 37:30.610
Let's go home.

37:47.990 --> 37:50.010
I figured Riyan might've felt guilty

37:50.240 --> 37:51.530
and left me a spirit artifact.

37:52.070 --> 37:53.130
Total letdown.

37:54.110 --> 37:54.780
Xiuyuan,

37:55.380 --> 37:56.420
why'd you stick around?

37:57.940 --> 37:58.820
Because you stayed.

38:03.340 --> 38:04.940
You could've gone your separate way.

38:06.240 --> 38:06.940
After all,

38:08.110 --> 38:09.860
we can't stay together forever.

38:11.150 --> 38:12.010
Why can't we?

38:17.510 --> 38:18.340
Our bond won't fade.

38:19.670 --> 38:20.610
We won't leave each other, living or dead.

38:35.110 --> 38:35.700
Lifei,

38:38.150 --> 38:39.420
I want to be with you forever,

38:42.420 --> 38:43.050
in this lifetime,

38:44.510 --> 38:45.340
and every next one.

38:59.550 --> 39:00.530
What're you talking about?

39:06.900 --> 39:07.650
Nothing much.

39:08.630 --> 39:09.450
What brings you here?

39:09.980 --> 39:11.610
They say you worked with the monster clan

39:11.630 --> 39:12.340
and broke them out of prison.

39:12.670 --> 39:13.860
Don't head back to Duanming City.

39:14.550 --> 39:15.820
I covered our tracks the whole trip.

39:16.820 --> 39:17.740
Who ratted her out?

39:18.340 --> 39:18.900
No clue.

39:19.240 --> 39:20.090
The elders plan

39:20.110 --> 39:21.380
to question Lifei severely.

39:25.190 --> 39:25.940
This is bad.

39:26.380 --> 39:27.900
Hide out with me at Xingzheng Hall for now.

39:28.590 --> 39:29.820
Running off now

39:30.590 --> 39:31.940
would make me look guilty on the run.

39:33.820 --> 39:35.170
I didn't slip up at all last night.

39:35.190 --> 39:36.260
I'll just deny it.

39:36.940 --> 39:37.860
It won't be easy to get away with.

39:38.420 --> 39:39.530
Cuixuan and my uncle

39:39.780 --> 39:41.010
will see right through our lies.

39:41.460 --> 39:43.570
What if they torture you to talk?

39:43.900 --> 39:45.050
They wouldn't do that.

39:45.720 --> 39:47.450
Those sect elders

39:47.780 --> 39:50.170
torture a weak girl

39:50.190 --> 39:51.170
to get a fake confession?

39:51.380 --> 39:52.570
That's cruel.

39:53.190 --> 39:54.220
And it'll be very embarrassing

39:54.670 --> 39:56.050
if everyone finds out.

39:59.070 --> 39:59.860
But what if they do?

40:00.550 --> 40:01.420
We'll team up

40:01.550 --> 40:02.490
and get through anything.

40:12.820 --> 40:14.420
I hunted monster beasts all night

40:14.510 --> 40:15.530
and did my job properly.

40:15.670 --> 40:16.900
How do I suddenly become a demon spy?

40:18.190 --> 40:18.820
Mr. Luo,

40:19.190 --> 40:20.860
we met last night, didn't we?

40:21.240 --> 40:22.530
I saw you last night,

40:23.190 --> 40:24.420
but you reeked

40:24.630 --> 40:25.820
of evil spiritual energy back then.

40:27.820 --> 40:28.820
That just means

40:29.030 --> 40:30.820
I was fighting monster beasts hard.

40:33.670 --> 40:35.010
Lifei stuck with the group

40:35.510 --> 40:36.490
and hunted monster beasts

40:36.980 --> 40:37.740
straight through till morning.

40:38.630 --> 40:39.820
You two have long been close friends.

40:39.940 --> 40:40.740
You might be lying

40:40.940 --> 40:41.820
to cover for one another.

40:43.030 --> 40:43.740
Qin,

40:44.420 --> 40:46.300
you mean we're covering each other,

40:47.030 --> 40:48.820
and that makes me a spy, too?

40:52.980 --> 40:55.450
I followed the evil spiritual energy last night

40:55.940 --> 40:57.300
and was jumped halfway.

40:57.900 --> 40:58.940
Jiang Lifei's the one

40:59.340 --> 41:00.490
who attacked me.

41:01.980 --> 41:02.740
Qin,

41:02.980 --> 41:04.380
you've hated me ever since what happened

41:04.420 --> 41:05.420
at Lilie Valley.

41:05.940 --> 41:07.130
If you want to get even,

41:07.240 --> 41:08.340
fight me fair and square.

41:09.070 --> 41:11.130
Quit stabbing me in the back.

41:11.460 --> 41:12.340
You're disgracing Wuyue Court

41:12.380 --> 41:13.490
and Elder Cuixuan.

41:13.720 --> 41:14.130
You!

41:14.150 --> 41:14.970
Yangling,

41:15.820 --> 41:17.970
you said she attacked you.

41:19.380 --> 41:20.420
Got any evidence?

41:20.900 --> 41:21.610
I'm sure

41:22.240 --> 41:24.300
that energy is definitely hers.

41:26.510 --> 41:27.380
Qin,

41:27.980 --> 41:29.050
I didn't know

41:29.470 --> 41:30.740
you thought about me so much

41:30.780 --> 41:31.490
that you see me

41:31.510 --> 41:32.420
in everyone now.

41:33.720 --> 41:35.340
She's the demon spy.

41:41.070 --> 41:41.650
It's her!

41:41.940 --> 41:43.450
She dressed up like one of us from the Wanxian Sect

41:43.720 --> 41:45.010
and knocked us out with drugs.

41:45.420 --> 41:46.530
Did you actually see me drug you?

41:47.150 --> 41:48.740
No, we didn't.

41:49.470 --> 41:50.340
But right after you walked past,

41:50.550 --> 41:51.380
we passed out.

41:52.460 --> 41:54.300
You were all lazing around

41:54.340 --> 41:55.010
and sleeping on duty.

41:55.030 --> 41:55.820
That's why the monster beasts got away.

41:55.860 --> 41:56.420
Now

41:56.820 --> 41:57.490
you're scared of taking the blame,

41:57.590 --> 41:58.380
so you lie and pin it on me?

41:59.150 --> 41:59.820
Well... I...

42:00.590 --> 42:01.490
Speaking of which,

42:01.720 --> 42:03.220
you really did have

42:03.240 --> 42:04.970
our Wanxian Sect outer robe on that night.

42:05.300 --> 42:06.090
Why was that?

42:10.460 --> 42:11.260
This is all on me.

42:13.470 --> 42:14.530
Lifei only took

42:14.720 --> 42:15.780
such a risky action to visit

42:17.340 --> 42:18.340
my uncle for my sake.

42:18.470 --> 42:20.090
You're from Wuyue Court.

42:20.240 --> 42:21.340
What were you doing

42:21.720 --> 42:23.700
visiting Mr. Xuanshan late at night?

42:31.550 --> 42:32.970
I wanted to form a cultivation partnership with Lifei,

42:33.720 --> 42:35.010
but I feared that my uncle wouldn't agree.

42:37.340 --> 42:38.450
She panicked

42:38.860 --> 42:40.050
and went straight in to ask why.

42:42.050 --> 42:42.300
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.300 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
